props.name: text
props.description: Text to use within the warning text component. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: iconFallbackText
props.description: The fallback text for the icon, used by screen readers and other assistive technologies.

slots.name: default
slots.description: HTML to use within the warning text component. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
